## Brute Force (For Understanding)

```java
import java.util.*;

class Solution {

    public int thirdMax(int[] nums) {

        TreeSet<Integer> set = new TreeSet<>();

        for (int num : nums) {
            set.add(num);
        }

        if (set.size() < 3) {
            return set.last();
        }

        set.pollLast();
        set.pollLast();

        return set.last();
    }
}
```

### Brute Force Complexity

* **Time Complexity:** `O(n log n)`
* **Space Complexity:** `O(n)`

